<ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</ENAMEX> of the reasons <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Bush</ENAMEX> administration aides are anxious to insist that the coming meeting will be informal is to avoid comparisons with the last such loosely structured superpower gathering , former President <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Reagan</ENAMEX> 's <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1986</ENAMEX> meeting with Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Gorbachev</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Reykjavik</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Iceland</ENAMEX> .
